overview.longBusinessSummary: SES AI Corporation develops and produces AI enhanced lithium metal and lithium ion rechargeable battery technologies for electric vehicles, urban air mobility, drones, robotics, battery energy storage systems, and other applications. It manufactures and sells li metal battery cells and battery materials, such as electrolytes for automotive original equipment manufacturers. SES AI Corporation operates in the United States and the Asia Pacific region. The company was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Woburn, Massachusetts.
